data.description: Charming 3 bedroom, 1 bathroom newly updated home! Inviting entry opens into bright living area that flows seamlessly into dining area. Kitchen boasts statement backsplash and appliances. Bedrooms are spacious and spilling with gorgeous natural light with the primary boasting a large walk in closet. Updates to this property include repaired water intrusion, gutters installed, exterior walls insulated, freshly painted walls and trim, updated windows, LVP flooring throughout. Large fenced backyard with a workshop is perfect for entertaining and furry friends. Wonderful location on the south side of Aiken, come see all this property has to offer to make it your own!
